== How to Compile ==

g++ Scene.cpp -lGL -lglut -o app

== How to use ==

Q	Exit
A	Paint a star
S	Paint a sphere
D	Cube
F	Cone
G	Torus
T 	Cylinder
Z	Move camera to the left
V	Move camera to the right
X	Move forward the camera
C	Move backward with the camera
H	Move selected figure in +x direction
Y	Move selected figure in -x direction
J	Move selected figure in +y direction
U	Move selected figure in -y direction
K	Move selected figure in +z direction
I	Move selected figure in -z direction

O	Select previous figure
P	Select next figure

Arrows	Rotate selected figure
M	Activate grid
N	Activate axes
Right Click other features as well
